* FatAttr-1.0 for Windows *
===========================

What is it?
-----------
FatAttr: Display or change attributes on a filesystem

Description
-----------
fatattr displays or changes attributes on an MS-Windows filesystem. If only a list of diles (or directories) are given, it displays the attributes for those files or directories. If given a list of attributes, it will add (+) or remove (-) the specified attributes from the given list of files or directories.
	 
